title: Angaaray
subTitle: While working undercover to take down a gang of killers, a hotshot policeman runs into his childhood friends, who have gone far too long down the criminal path.

title: Kurukshetra
subTitle: ACP Prithviraj, an honest man, arrests Chief Minister Baburao's son for raping a woman. Consequently, Baburao leaves no stone unturned to get revenge against Prithviraj.

title: Issaq
subTitle: In the kaleidoscopic cityscapes of Banaras, a soul-stirring Romeo-and-Juliet-esque romance kindles between two young individuals from rival mafia families.

title: Fillers
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of promotional videos and trailers of Bollywood movies featuring popular actors and actresses.

title: Hameshaa
subTitle: Raja and Reshma fall in love but Yash, Raja's childhood friend, likes Reshma so he kills Raja. Years later, the trio is born again to rewrite their stories.

title: Main Prem Ki Diwani Hoon
subTitle: Sanjana falls in love with Prem Kishen after mistaking him for his boss, Prem Kumar, whom she is actually supposed to marry. But, the relationship is threatened when Prem Kishen reveals the truth.

title: Loha
subTitle: After a bid to arrest Sher Singh fails, officer Dayal is crippled and his partner Amar's career is sabotaged. When Amar gets another chance to nab Sher Singh, he hires two crooks for the job.

title: Henna
subTitle: Henna, a bubbly young woman based in a village in Pakistan, sets her heart on an endearing stranger who winds up there with serious injuries and no memory of his past.

title: Dacait
subTitle: After being mercilessly beaten and abandoned to die, a young man is rescued by a band of dacoits, who nurse him back to health in their hidden lair.

title: Judaai
subTitle: Shashikant and Gauri get married in honour of his late father's will. But, marital problems soon arise when Gauri suspects him of having an affair, leading to a chain of misunderstandings.

title: Cirkus
subTitle: Two sets of identical twins are separated at birth and grow in two different cities. Years later, chaos ensues when one set of twins decides to visit the town where the other runs a circus.

title: Cirkus
subTitle: Two sets of identical twins are separated at birth and grow in two different cities. Years later, chaos ensues when one set of twins decides to visit the town where the other runs a circus.

title: Ghayal Once Again
subTitle: The lionhearted Ajay Mehra once again takes up the mantle of justice in a troubled society where the powerful believe they can get away with any crime.

title: Rehnaa Hai Terre Dil Mein
subTitle: Maddy has seven days to win Reena's affections before she finds out that he is not Rajeev, the childhood friend and prospective fiance she has been expecting.

title: Yaarana
subTitle: Childhood friends Bishan and Kishan are separated by Bishan's uncle. However, Bishan helps Kishan to become a successful singer, and Kishan uses his skills to restore Bishan's lost fortune.

title: King Uncle
subTitle: Ashok, an austere man, experiences a profound shift in his life when an orphan girl enters his world, infusing it with warmth and meaning that he had long forgotten.

title: Sandwich
subTitle: Sher Singh has two wives, Nisha and Sweety, and juggles his time between them. However, when his two wives cross paths, his troubles increase manifold leading to hilarious situations.

title: Jaan
subTitle: Karan is hired to kill Kajal, the granddaughter of a police commissioner, but they end up falling in love. However, fate tests their bond when Karan's true intentions are revealed.

title: Ajay
subTitle: Manorama falls in love with Ajay, even though they come from different social backgrounds. They want to get married, but Manorama's uncles try their best to separate the happy couple.

title: Prem Rog
subTitle: After a series of tragedies shake Manorama's life, Devdhar, her childhood friend who falls for her, vows to make her happy. In the process, he faces the wrath of Manorama's conservative family.

title: Jurmana
subTitle: A flambouyant businessman places a bet with his former college friend to woo their professor's young daughter. However, the bet leads to a series of unexpected consequences.

title: Jurmana
subTitle: A flambouyant businessman places a bet with his former college friend to woo their professor's young daughter. However, the bet leads to a series of unexpected consequences.

title: Bachchan Pandey
subTitle: To succeed in the film industry, Myra chooses Bachchhan Paandey, a notorious hooligan, as the main focus of her new movie. Things get complicated when the gangster decides to act in the film.

title: Pukar
subTitle: Major Jaidev saves a politician from the clutches of a dreaded terrorist. However, the terrorist joins hands with his childhood friend Anjali to ruin his life.

title: Laat Saab
subTitle: Vijay and Anju love each other, but she leaves a note behind and sets off to Bombay. Vijay follows her but is told that she died three years ago and her lookalike mysteriously reappears in his life.

title: Ek Aur Ek Gyarah
subTitle: Tara and Sitara, siblings and small-time con-men, are on the run from a wanted criminal after they accidentally shoot at him. Soon they end up at the house of major Ram Singh, where they take refuge.

title: Loafer
subTitle: Ravi, an unemployed man who constantly gets into fights, is framed for the murder of a gangster. With no support from his family, he must now fight to prove his innocence.

title: Bol Radha Bol
subTitle: While Kishen enjoys village life and romance with Radha, a sinister doppelganger plots. Upon returning home, he'll discover his identity and life stolen by this malevolent impostor.

title: Andha Kanoon
subTitle: Two siblings, Vijay and Durga, vow to avenge the death of their parents. So, Durga becomes an inspector to punish the criminals, whereas Vijay breaks the law to achieve his goal.

title: Chaalbaaz
subTitle: Anju endures mistreatment at home, whereas her long-separated twin Manju boldly navigates life's challenges. By some quirk of fate, they end up trading places, and their worlds erupt in chaos.

title: Apaharan
subTitle: Ajay, an aspiring policeman, borrows money from a moneylender to pursue his dream. However, he is unable to repay the loan on time and decides to be a part of a kidnapping scheme.
